longBusinessSummary: Impact Coatings AB (publ) provides coating solutions using PVD technology in Sweden, China, the United States, South Korea, and Germany. The company offers INLINECOATER PVD coating systems; and electrolyzers and fuel cell coatings. It also provides provides coating, support, maintenance, and consumables and spare parts services. The company's products are use in electrolyzers, fuel cells, radomes, waveguide antennas, and decorative applications. Impact Coatings AB (publ) was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Linköping, Sweden.
